OL,3,CPost Office scandal: Police chief not
OL,4,Cruling out corporate manslaughter
OL,6,FMet Police Commander Stephen Clayman
OL,7,Fhas told ITV News he's 'confident' of
OL,8,Fresults from its large-scale probe
OL,9,Finto the Post Office scandal, as
OL,10,FInvestigations Editor Daniel Hewitt
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThe police commander in charge of the
OL,14,Fcriminal investigation into the Post
OL,15,FOffice scandal has told ITV News he is
OL,16,F"confident" and "optimistic of good
OL,17,Fresults" as he revealed the number of
OL,18,Fsuspects is growing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
