OL,3,CPost Office scandal: Police chief not
OL,4,Cruling out corporate manslaughter
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview, his first
OL,7,Fsince taking the role, Commander
OL,8,FStephen Clayman said the
OL,9,Finvestigation, which involves 100
OL,10,Fofficers from forces across the
OL,11,Fcountry, is not ruling out corporate
OL,12,Fmanslaughter charges against the Post
OL,13,FOffice.
OL,15,F"We're focusing on perjury and
OL,16,Fperverting justice, but I'm not ruling
OL,17,Fout other offences if that evidence
OL,18,Fcomes to light," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
