OL,6,FHe also told ITV News that police had
OL,7,Fexperienced "difficulties" with the
OL,8,FPost Office, describing their
OL,9,Fcooperation with the criminal inquiry
OL,10,Fin handing over documents as "not as
OL,11,Ffast as I would certainly like". He
OL,12,Fsaid the police prepared to go to
OL,13,Fcourt if potential evidence is not
OL,14,Fhanded to them.
