OL,6,FCommander Clayman said that "dozens"
OL,7,Fof people were being treated as
OL,8,F"persons of interest". Asked if former
OL,9,FChief Executive Paula Vennells was one
OL,10,Fof them, he said he wouldn't comment
OL,11,Fon individuals, but reassured sub-
OL,12,Fpostmasters that officers would be
OL,13,Fgoing after senior bosses to see if
OL,14,F"offences extend into management".
OL,16,FCommander Stephen Clayman says he is
OL,17,F"confident" the investigation will
OL,18,Fhave good results
