OL,6,FAny criminal trials are not expected
OL,7,Fto take place until 2027 at the
OL,8,Fearliest, as police are waiting for
OL,9,Fthe conclusion of the Public Inquiry
OL,10,Finto the Horizon scandal.
OL,12,FCommander Clayman said the police
OL,13,Finvestigation also involves at least
OL,14,F3,000 victims and around 1.5 million
OL,15,Fdocuments.
OL,17,FThe force has said there are now 100
OL,18,Fofficers from across the country
OL,19,Fworking on the investigation, dubbed
OL,20,FOperation Olympos.
