OL,6,FDecisions to charge anyone over
OL,7,Fpotential criminal offences are on
OL,8,Fhold until the public inquiry's final
OL,9,Freport is published, police added - a
OL,10,Fdecision criticised by former sub-
OL,11,Fpostmasters like Harjinder Butoy.
OL,13,F"There's enough evidence there for
OL,14,Fthem to continue," Mr Butoy told ITV
OL,15,FNews.
OL,17,F"They don't really have to wait for
OL,18,Fthe public inquiry because they've got
OL,19,Fall the paperwork for it. I just don't
OL,20,Funderstand why it's taking so long."
