OL,3,CPost Office scandal: Police chief not
OL,4,Cruling out corporate manslaughter
OL,6,FMore than 900 sub-postmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,9,F2000 and 2015, as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,FHorizon system made it seem money had
OL,11,Fgone missing at their branches. The
OL,12,Fscandal has since been considered one
OL,13,Fof Britain's most widespread
OL,14,Fmiscarriages of justice in history.
OL,16,FHe told ITV News: "I want someone
OL,17,Fcharged, sent to prison the way they
OL,18,Fsent me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
