OL,6,F"It really destroyed me and probably a
OL,7,Flot of other people out there. I
OL,8,Freally want that to happen, but will
OL,9,Fit happen? I don't think it will."
OL,11,FCommander Clayman said he had taken
OL,12,Fthe time to meet with sub-postmasters
OL,13,Fin person to discuss the investigation.
OL,15,F"I've looked them in the eyes and said
OL,16,Fwe're going to do our very best to get
OL,17,Fan outcome for them and being very
OL,18,Fopen and honest about the challenges
OL,19,Fof that," he said.
