OL,6,F"I have said this directly to them
OL,7,Fbecause I wanted to make them aware of
OL,8,Fwhat we're doing and why we're doing
OL,9,Fit, which is to try and bring some
OL,10,Fresolution to what awful experience
OL,11,Fthey have had to endure for so many
OL,12,Fyears."
OL,14,FNo timetable has been set for release
OL,15,Fof the final report from the Post
OL,16,FOffice Horizon IT Inquiry, but its
OL,17,Fclosing statements will be heard on
OL,18,FDecember 16 and 17.
