OL,6,FIn November, the Met said four
OL,7,Fsuspects had been identified in the
OL,8,Finvestigation, a number which is
OL,9,Fexpected to rise.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, hundreds of sub-postmasters
OL,12,Fare still yet to receive compensation,
OL,13,Fincluding Mr Butoy. The government has
OL,14,Fannounced three main payout schemes,
OL,15,Fbut those impacted in the scandal have
OL,16,Fsuffered delays in receiving money.
OL,18,FIn October, a parliamentary inquiry
OL,19,Fwas announced to look into delays in
OL,20,Fcompensation.
