OL,6,FMr Butoy told ITV News of his anger
OL,7,Fwaiting to see those responsible for
OL,8,Fthe wrongful convictions face
OL,9,Fprosecution themselves.
OL,11,F"You think it's going to go away, but
OL,12,Fit doesn't, does it? It's right in me,
OL,13,Fit's because I want justice. I want
OL,14,Fsomeone done. These people have done
OL,15,Fme, they've done my family over. Not
OL,16,Fjust mine, but hundreds of people out
OL,17,Fthere."
